#                before commit
#              • **SOCKS5 proxy local bind** so any
#                proxy-aware app can route through the MASQUE tunnel
#              • **automatic re-scan** + reconnect on tunnel failure
#              • **config.json persistence** across runs (the
#                Cloudflare WARP-style enrollment is cached locally
#                instead of re-registering every launch)
